msgctxt "1520"
msgid "Dainty Villager"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1524"
msgid "Saejima"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72_Dainty Villager"
msgid "You're that guy staying with Okudera-san, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84_Saejima"
msgid "Yeah."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "96_Dainty Villager"
msgid "Why'd you come up to the mountains? You don't look like you came to hunt. Nobody in the village has seen you before, either."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "108_Saejima"
msgid "Uh, I usually hunt in a different area."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "120_Dainty Villager"
msgid "No kidding? Well, the road is snowed over, so you're stuck here for a while."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "132_Dainty Villager"
msgid "We don't have TV, there's no radio reception, and we don't get newspapers. You'll probably be bored out of your skull, but just sit tight."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "144_Saejima"
msgid "Okay. Got it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "156_Saejima"
msgid "(No TV or newspapers, huh? Lucky for me. The prison break's probably all over the news.)"
msgstr ""

